description: Unity Vegan Kitchen is a gourmet food trailer in Austin, offering eclectic eats made from scratch on the premises. This menu uses locally-sourced and organic ingredients whenever possible, and consists of such favorites as the house specialty lasagne, sandwiches prepared on bread that is baked daily, and a mouthwatering pineapple cobbler based on a family recipe. With all this delicious vegan food, and gluten free options as well, nobody will be bereft of delicious food when they stop by Unity!
name: Unity Vegan Kitchen
